<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0780 </DOCNO><TEXT>This book discusses the following contents: Properties and characteristicsof loose solids. Flow properties and handling of granular and powderedsolids. Rheological behavior of fluidized solids. Hydrodynamics of fluidization.Hydrodynamics of entrainment. Commercial fluid bed processes. Coal gasification.Coal liquefaction. Principles of fluid bed reactor modeling. Experimentalmethods. Vertical flow of particulate solids in standpipes and risers.Pneumatic transport. Gas premixing techniques. Particulate capture-drymethods. Particulate capture and venturi scrubbers.</TEXT></DOC>